Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:58.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願っても何もできないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}わかってはいるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}失う怖さが邪魔をしても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.58,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}誰しも明日へ向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}見えない 知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}自由も愛も与えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}さぁ選べ  舞い降りた天使達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}感じる予感に Shoot the arrow of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:21.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}翼に意志を 身を委ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}倦まず弛まず
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}ただ 生きてたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}もう いっそ嘘でもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}正義を貫く 最後で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:34.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}「幸せになりたい」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:42.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}ただそれだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}It ain’t over till it’s over(Shoot!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}勇往邁進 GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:58.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}即使祈愿 也什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.41,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}明明知道如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.12,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}哪怕失去的恐惧作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.58,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}人们还是会走向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.75,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}看不见 不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.21,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}给他自由与爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.34,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}好了 选择吧 飞舞降临的天使们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.26,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}向察觉的预感 射出命运之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:21.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}灌注意志于翅膀  委身于它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.01,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}不知疲倦 从不松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}只是 想要活着而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}不管了 就算撒谎也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.27,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}贯穿正义 到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:34.19,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}说一句「我想要幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:42.70,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.95,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}它不会结束 直到它结束 (发射!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.75,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}勇往直前 GO!
